title: Living Food Lab
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Organic, Western, Salad bar, Juice bar, All Raw
description: A teaching kitchen located at Green School helping to raise consciousness around food choices through food, classes, and community outreach. Serves living foods, picked that morning, such as raw pizza, raw mango and spinach wrap, fresh juices, choose-you-own salad bar, and raw desserts. All vegan except for honey.
